  "commit_message": "feat(ui): KEV badges on analysis, changelog, home and trend surfaces (#137)\n\nExtend CISA KEV visibility from the release/artifact views to the four\nfollow-up surfaces: Vulnerability Analysis, component/organization\nchangelogs, the AppHome most-vulnerable-components widget, and the\nfindings-over-time chart drilldown.\n\nThese surfaces sit on expensive backend computations (changelog\ndiffing, findingsPerDay, mostVulnerableComponentsPerOrg), so instead\nof the mirror-query pattern a new kevFieldSelect",
